name: Number 89: Computerbeast Diablosis
desc:
2 Level 7 monsters
Once per turn: You can detach 1 material from this card; look at your opponent's Extra Deck, also banish 1 monster from their Extra Deck face-down. At the end of the Battle Phase, if this card destroyed a monster by battle: You can target 1 card in your opponent's GY; banish it face-down. If a card(s) in your opponent's possession is banished face-down (except during the Damage Step): You can banish cards from the top of your opponent's Deck face-down, equal to the number of their face-down banished cards. You can only use this effect of "Number 89: Computerbeast Diablosis" once per turn.
